1 (a2) It shall be unlawful for any person to use the title "APRN" or "APRN" plus their
2 respective role titles, the role title alone, authorized abbreviations, or any other title that would
3 lead a person to believe the individual is an APRN, unless permitted by this act.
4 …."
5 SECTION 4. No later than October 1, 2025, the North Carolina Board of Nursing
6 shall adopt temporary rules to implement the provisions of Section 3 of this act. Those temporary
7 rules shall remain in effect until permanent rules are adopted to replace the temporary rules.
8 SECTION 5. Sections 1 and 3 of this act are effective October 1, 2025. The
9 remainder of this act is effective when it becomes law.
